    "name": "Elder Thing",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Known by various names on various worlds, but most often as \u201celder things\u201d or \u201cold ones,\u201d these alien creatures are interested in creating lasting works of art, architecture, and even life (such as the dreaded shoggoths). They possess a boundless capacity for war and egotism.<br/><br/>A typical elder thing is 6 feet tall from head to foot, with a 7-foot wingspan. Surprisingly heavy for its size, an elder thing generally weighs about 450 pounds."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This strange being has a star-shaped head and numerous writhing appendages arranged radially around its barrel-shaped body.</i>",
